benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/invoicePayments/{paymentId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to payment

covered: Valid Request: Scenarios TC01-TC04, TC17, TC20 cover updates with valid payloads and data integrity.
Non-Existing Resource: TC06 covers 404 for missing resource.
Server Error Handling: TC12 tests 500 on dependency failure.
Validation: TC05, TC07, TC08, TC09, TC10, TC13 cover various invalid inputs and malformed body.
Edge Cases & Robustness: TC14-TC16 cover large payloads, max length, extra properties.
Data Integrity: TC17 verifies after-update GET returns updated data.
Duplicate Handling: TC18 tests duplicate field names.
Performance & Concurrency: TC19-TC20 cover concurrent requests and performance considerations.
gaps: Partial Update semantics not explicitly tested (PUT vs PATCH).
Rate Limiting and throttling scenarios not covered.
Role-based access variations beyond unauthorized test (e.g., 403 for insufficient permissions).
recommendations: Add a test for explicit partial update behavior or confirm PUT semantics vs PATCH.
Introduce rate-limiting tests to validate throttling and throughput.
Add caching tests to verify ETag/Cache-Control headers and cache invalidation on updates.
Expand authorization tests to cover forbidden scenarios for restricted roles.
